data.description: Brick Ranch Home, Southwest Sedalia Near Katy park and Trail!  Large living room with tiled entrance. Nice eat in kitchen with breakfast bar, ceramic tile floors and all appliances included.  Master suite has walk-in-closet, ceiling fan and half-bath. Second, third bedroom and full bathroom on main level. Family room with brick, wood burning fireplace and door to back patio. Central heating and cooling system with heat pump. Full basement could be finished for additional living space.  Beautiful, fenced backyard with seating area and firepit. Great location close to Katy trail and a park that offers walking trail, skatepark, baseball fields and playground. Easy access to South 65 Hwy and Part of skyline school district.
